name: Cargolux 747-8F takeoff from Calgary
description:
Unnaturally quiet O_o
This is a Cargolux Airlines International Boeing 747-8F departing Calgary, bound for Luxembourg. This flight was quite late arriving, as it normally comes in at around midnight.
